readable.content: A dog jumps up towards a woman in a car , while another dog is outside the car . An orange dog and a little white dog with black spots are next to a white car . A small black and white dog jumps at a woman in a white jeep while a golden dog follows beside them . A small dog jumps by a car to reach a lady 's face while another dog watches . White and black dog jumps at someone through car window .
